T1  - Note—A Multiple-Item Inventory Model with a Job Completion Criterion
AU  - Graves, Stephen C.
Y1  - 1982/11/01
PY  - 1982
DA  - 1982/11/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.28.11.1334
DO  - 10.1287/mnsc.28.11.1334
